 having a <b>50% off</b> recurring discount, which does seem even cheaper! The \u201cmini\u201d VPS in <a href=\"http://vzlayer.com/metered.html\">their metered VPS range</a> is now <b>$3.98/month</b> when you use promo code <b>LOWLOWLOW</b>. <a href=\"http://www.vzlayer.com/clients/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=11&amp;promocode=LOWLOWLOW\">Order this package here</a>.</p><ul><li>256MB guaranteed/512MB burstable memory</li><li>25GB storage</li><li>250GB/month data transfer</li><li>OpenVZ/SolusVM</li></ul><p>Servers are with BurstNet in Scranton PA. Rick and his services <a href=\"http://rikemedia.com/\">Rike Media</a> is based in UK.</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fvzlayer-3-98-256mb-openvz-vps%2F&amp;t=VZLayer%20-%20%243.98%20256MB%20OpenVZ%20VPS\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=VZLayer%20-%20%243.98%20256MB%20OpenVZ%20VPS&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fvzlayer-3-98-256mb-openvz-vps%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fvzlayer-3-98-256mb-openvz-vps%2F&amp;title=VZ